<a name="content"></a><p class="lead"><strong>If you want format text into columns or rows inside of your document, the best way to do this is to use a table.</strong></p class="lead"> 

<p>A <strong>table</strong> is the placement of text into
columns and rows. It may be one column or one row or many. A very common
example of a table is found is many books, the table of contents which lists
the topics in the book.</p>

<p>A table can be easily inserted into a document. Be sure to first place your cursor in the document where you want to put the table!</p>

<p>Inserting tables is a little different in the various versions.</p> 


